   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "# Runge-Kutta 1ª Ordem\n",
    "\n",
    "Também conhecido como método de Euler"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 601,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "def runge_kutta_1st_order(f, t0, y0, h, n):\n",
    "    t = t0\n",
    "    y = y0\n",
    "    resultados = []\n",
    "    for i in range  (1, n):\n",
    "        y = y + h * f(t, y)\n",
    "        t = t + h\n",
    "    resultados.append(y)\n",
    "    return resultados\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "# RK-2"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 602,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "def runge_kutta_2nd_order(f, t0, y0, h, n):\n",
    "    t = t0\n",
    "    y = y0\n",
    "    \n",
    "    for i in range(1,n):\n",
    "        k1 = h * f(t, y)\n",
    "        k2 = h * f(t + h, y + k1)\n",
    "        y = y + (k1 + k2) / 2\n",
    "        t = t + h\n",
    "    \n",
    "    return y"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "# RK-3"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 603,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "def runge_kutta_3rd_order(f, t0, y0, h, n):\n",
    "    t = t0\n",
    "    y = y0\n",
    "    \n",
    "    for i in range(1,n):\n",
    "        k1= h * f(t, y)\n",
    "        k2= h * f(t + h/2, y + k1/2)\n",
    "        k3= h * f(t + h, y - k1 + 2*k2)\n",
    "        y =y + (k1 + 4*k2 + k3) / 6\n",
    "        t =t + h\n",
    "    \n",
    "    return y\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "# RK-4"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 604,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "def runge_kutta_4th_order(f, t0, y0, h, n):\n",
    "    t = t0\n",
    "    y = y0\n",
    "    \n",
    "    for i in range(1,n):\n",
    "        k1= h * f(t, y)\n",
    "        k2= h * f(t + h/2, y + k1/2)\n",
    "        k3= h * f(t + h/2, y + k2/2)\n",
    "        k4= h * f(t + h, y + k3)\n",
    "        \n",
    "        y =y + (k1 + 2*k2 + 2*k3 + k4) / 6\n",
    "        t =t + h\n",
    "    \n",
    "    return y\n"
   ]
  },
